Chaoyi Huang ontributed from OCI to K8S to OpenStack. He created innovative memory overcommit technology and designed algorithm to detect performance degradation for co-located VMs, found phenomenon similar as " Newton's law of motion" in instruction execution.  As the first chief architect, he designed Huawei cloud IEF, the code base of CNCF KubeEdge. He worked in both cloud and telco industry.

